Comment: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:11.78,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好厉害的水光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里是球磨川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野出来竟然是这样的风景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你别破坏气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,其实你也是很激动的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不看着你的脸真看不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,激动怎么可能表现在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,突然就跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你那双手是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:35.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,揉揉×N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的是 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,呐 池袋要多久才到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,朝发夕至吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,连黑豹车队都到不了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明天肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:52.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是之前只花了一个小时就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算现在比以前「拉伸」了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但也没什么到达不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你这太乐观了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是就这么无忧无虑毫无计划地过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,十有八九会在某个地方被团灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要这么说 可能明天早上突然就发现 啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我已经到达池袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,或许不是明天就到 而是需要三天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.61,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最快也应该需要一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,可能更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就半个月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:19.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留肯定会考虑到这一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,听听她怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.89,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,呐 到达需要几天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.15,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分心驾驶很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:30.14,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好了 静留刚刚学会开火车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:30.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 车速是不是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.08,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,能不能放缓一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:46.79,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我虽然在努力 但速度根本降不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.66,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,弯道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,弯道 弯道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,又是弯道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:03:59.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,弯道×N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,超弯的路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.74,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真实感觉「勿忘你終有一死」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你没事了吗 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:28.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎教我的时候 我以为是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他突然变回正常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然每天只有五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然后就教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且还变成了一个帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.17,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 说谎是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 我说的是真的 绝对真实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然我怎么学会开火车的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生之前可是铁道公司的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我以为只是吹牛来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但竟然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,五分钟能够变回来 是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是帽子 驾驶员的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把它给他戴上之后就变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,听我说 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.88,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说谎是真的不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我发四我发四
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,绝对是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然我绝对不会开火车的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,Trust Me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再说了 你是真的开往池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们没有走错方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:11.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那边是秩父市对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以这边就是往池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,噢 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.07,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:23.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,听说池袋 有模特和执事管家对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有侦探啥的 杀人犯之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:29.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是麻痹大意 被刺 被拐 被骗都可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,痛痛痒痒 时髦流行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这是什么刻板印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还要提防宰客行为噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实 你有带钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我可是好好存起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:39.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,挺好 有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的储蓄罐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有两万日元吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不对 我的储蓄罐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我的储蓄罐落在家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,噢 她忘在家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我一共就两百五十日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你带了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,个人信息是不会告诉你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,让我借用一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,借贷什么的我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小柒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我倒是带了点钱 可以借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你是我的神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你能借我多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我就带了三千多日元 借你一千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:09.95,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别扯 这可是巨款
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这上面写了什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果没有面包 就买点零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微感觉有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,远水救不了近火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是就是 就那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有一千二百五十日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要买些什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,首先还是先买点能吃的食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我想买点奶茶之类喝喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有来份奶油蒜香烧鸡 还有法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是这些 要更加普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,买点罐头食品或是罐装面包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子 你莫得梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我们什么都没有携带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们放学之后就直接上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们没有任何吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,稍微一点的话 我还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的吗 太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说了要做好准备的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,能看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,果然生存 需要最低限度的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,香板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是用来量取意大利面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以哪里有所谓的「意大利面」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这是练习穿的苏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么静留你带着这件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 我在我家里找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}让我看看 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 我没啥问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:12.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}吵架禁止 要好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 食物只剩下这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:19.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我记得我带了很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有就是那些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟是吾野的特产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咱不是很喜欢它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:32.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 我他妈在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:32.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的是 我不知道该怎么办了敲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 这种事情确实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「视野强化」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,没有比这更好的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要是能列个清单的话 应该就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们的财产 这些就是全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.58,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,内裤咋办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,女孩子什么的 不要说什么内裤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就底裤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.44,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是这个意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但实际上 我们不知道要多久才能到池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一直就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.91,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,卡斯蒂利亚女王伊莎贝尔 祈祷战争的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:10.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,说是九个月都没有更换过内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要是买不到的话 被葉香看见会被说教的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 你冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等到了东吾野后 再去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.84,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还要去储备一些食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且可以长期保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我肚子饿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:23.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:28.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在生存恐怖游戏中 食欲贪婪的胖子最先死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:28.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我才不胖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.28,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就只是现在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:32.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,忍耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,反正小晶你会说「我是最难伺候的一个吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,噢哦 被你抢先说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,有勇气屈服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:41.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还没有到吗 池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这问题问了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:54.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这有啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我很在意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你脑袋是真的笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:02.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你这种高高在上的态度真的太坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶小晶 眼泪汪晶晶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算我是爱哭鬼 那也是十年之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲实灵长类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我就考过一次零分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,而且还是小测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的是 你们两个别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,既然你那么讨厌 就在吾野等着算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我又没有说我讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要擅自给我作主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.26,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}小晶 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你不也自己选择乘坐这辆列车了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要不是玲实和抚子上来了 我才不会坐这班车的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个是 在那个时间节点迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都这样做的 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们没有必要跟我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我原本就打算自己一个人过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算静留你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,总感觉比平常生长得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,还有 雾气也浓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要告诉我已经过了东吾野了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,玲实 你视力挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你能看清楚那边有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么 你说什么恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什么呢 感觉没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:15.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:17.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什么东西要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:22.61,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是球磨水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.56,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,球磨水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:27.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是球磨川现存的 传说中的神秘龙首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是球磨水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,竟然是球磨水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.37,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这竟然 是电车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.71,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他绝对是杀人魔鬼来了结我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:03.10,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我就是球磨川史上最强的连环杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.69,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,喂 你太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个 你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我的名字并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.53,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀嘛 那个 我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.86,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我在球磨川来回穿梭 研究并记录了很多信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.06,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,好久没有见到任何人了 真的吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.27,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那啥 你们在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:31.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 我们 打算前往池袋来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,欸 池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:33.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这确实厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:35.43,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我可是从池袋过来这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.54,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我感觉你大有可为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你从池袋来的吗 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.71,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀 也没有那么厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋来的人我是第一次见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.64,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,额 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,西部呢 东部呢 中池袋公园呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋公交 动画咋样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,淳久堂书店呢 三省堂书店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有奶茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在最热门的咖啡店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你原来不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,但是有一件事情是可以确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 啥子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.49,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那就是7G事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:10.35,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那之后 沿着西部池袋线以外的世界全部都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.37,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如上 咱是推测大概感觉出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,推测 大概 感觉出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,东边的菌类高耸入云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.69,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,高调宣言要去征服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.17,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,而再往东边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:28.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,与山羊共存的野兽之名虽有所不同 但正是我要说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你到底想要说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,原来是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,无理荒诞的自我独白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以才感觉这么夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们应该走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.33,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.25,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶等会 等会等会等会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:44.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,总而言之 我不建议你们前去池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:49.87,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,总而言之这非常 非常地非常 非常不可能 我推测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如上是你所认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.34,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,敲 等会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.74,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,机会难得 稍微给我些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.84,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,来点礼物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.80,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我给你好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.67,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,交换
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好东西是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.64,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这个是我自己做的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.86,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,它超级有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:08.85,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我超推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.56,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,还有一句劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.08,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,什么东西都不要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:16.81,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,能够信任的只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.31,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,啊 我说的话例外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:19.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这种事情想逃也逃不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.18,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,好的感谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.17,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,把这个给他应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我想这是你父亲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们应该用不上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.20,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不是不是这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这难道就是文明的力量 加热非燃烧烟的烟仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 你要的话就给你算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.46,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,太感谢啦（多国语言）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,照顾好自己 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.59,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.53,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我会沿着球磨川 顺着西池袋线而上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.48,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,所有的谜题都会一一解明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.59,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶 等会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.59,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我才不是老爷爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.99,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我现在还很年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他是个挺奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是好久没有遇见过成年人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,除了猫哥他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,噢 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总感觉他像是卖护身符的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又可疑又虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还是第一次遇到 比善治郎先生还怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么善治郎先生不和我们一起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 不要 和他同行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不然睡在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你那种鼠目寸光的话就不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一起来的话 很多事情都能听他解释
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生说他不想离吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:29.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他无法离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:35.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他说他一离吾野 头痛和头晕就会加重非常厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说是因为软绵绵手术导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也许是暗示也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,暗示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好比是洗脑术或是催眠术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,软绵绵的状态 那么就很可能是一种暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但实际上可能并没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但实际上他头上确实有个印记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛总而言之 善治郎不一起来也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟增加一个人 储粮消耗也会增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但反过来说 静留你为什么决定要去池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这种事情 要是书面说明咱应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是为了葉香 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,因为没有吾野找到她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实 这种话没必要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咋了 我说错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对吗 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.72,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是因为在报纸上看到了她的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 差不多是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 但是你怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.28,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不会太勉强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,去池袋应该会轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香或许会跑过来说 好久不见 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,能这样最好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.88,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,听我说 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.55,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果静留你什么也不说就离开了吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:51.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就好像静留失去了葉香一样 大家也会为你而伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这点我倒是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:55.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那么 就再道歉一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:15:59.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说我们没必要和你一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:12.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香我们也是知道的 她也是我们的朋友呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 咱是真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我没有考虑到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你有这份心意就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,既然事情都解决了 我们现在就回吾野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为什么你会这么说呢 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 我们不是要做好准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:34.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,替换衣物 充足食物 毛毯 还有露营用品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 要是带些香薰蜡烛或许会更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,睡眠不足是压力的来源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不是 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们都到这里了还回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难道不浪费时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:48.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我们没有任何装备 确实是比较担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:52.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,再说了 我原本就不赞同这场所谓的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我们回到吾野以后 小晶就留在那看家算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,留我一个人绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.25,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,小雪姐 抱歉让您做这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那我要带上《高丘親王航海記》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实不知道的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:21.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我就带小晶你吃不了的墨西哥辣味薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,会很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,学校缺勤也必须要正确汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:28.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,实在不行 直接休学或许会更加好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那么我们准备出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,刚才这里还不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,水位竟然上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:50.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,刚刚那个卖护身符给的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:00.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 摩尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这个是摩尔斯电码
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:07.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我忘记让小雪奶奶帮我传达了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,摩尔斯电码吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是告诉善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.80,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,没有回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.48,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是说了每天下午五点准时和我联系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.35,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,这里是吾野 收到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,点 线 线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,能不能慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「收到」该咋回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你敲的对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不会是在瞎编吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:37.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.99,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,水位上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.32,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,也就是说在球磨川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,电车淹水危险 请开到高出避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:47.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我们到底应该走哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.02,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,光张嘴说话在这不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,前进或后退 征求意见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:03.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野和东吾野的海拔高度由国家地理研究院确定 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,已经过五分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底要怎么办 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:33.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就在我们后面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,冷静下来 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快点加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前进四
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但这不也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们只能继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:29.46,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,香薰蜡烛 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等到了池袋再带上也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明你只有一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,借我点钱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,绝不借贷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:39.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们真的要去池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,必须得去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我们已经别无选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:48.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你认为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,出发 去见葉香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,到东吾野站啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.47,ZH-Main-Down,Resident 1,0,0,0,,呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Resident 1,0,0,0,,欢迎来到东吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reisdent 2,0,0,0,,旅行者真的好少见呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.90,ZH-Main-Down,Resident 3,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.00,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,要不好好来放松一下吧
